			<h2 id="score-ranking">Score Ranking</h2>
			<p>Flags have the format hsma{.+}. You are required to submit the entire flag, including hsma{}, for score. If a flag looks different, it will be clarified in the challenge description.</p>

			<p>The score of each challenge will be dynamically calculated according to the number of solved teams.</p>

			<p>Final ranking is determined by the total score of each team. In case of multiple teams with equal scores, the team that reached the score earlier ranks higher.</p>

